### [Isaiah Chapter 10](../../../bib/kjv/isa010.htm#001.md)

that when

A permanent method in the divine government of the earth. Israel is
always the centre of the divine counsels earthward ([Deu
32:8](../../../bib/kjv/deu032.htm#008).md). The Gentile nations are
permitted to afflict Israel in chastisement for her national sins, but
invariably and inevitably retribution falls upon them. See; ([Gen
15:13](../../../bib/kjv/gen015.htm#013).md); ([Gen
15:14](../../../bib/kjv/gen015.htm#014).md); ([Deu
30:5-7](../../../bib/kjv/deu030.htm#005).md); ([Isa
14:1](../../../bib/kjv/isa014.htm#001).md); ([Isa
14:2](../../../bib/kjv/isa014.htm#002).md); ([Joe
3:1-8](../../../bib/kjv/joe003.htm#001).md); ([Mic
5:7-9](../../../bib/kjv/mic005.htm#007).md); ([Mat
25:31-40](../../../bib/kjv/mat025.htm#031).md).

[Isaiah 10:20](../../../bib/kjv/isa010.htm#020.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_020">isa 10:20</span></span>

that day

"That day": often the equivalent of "the day of the Lord" ([Isa
2:10-22](../../../bib/kjv/isa002.htm#010).md); ([Rev
19:11-21](../../../bib/kjv/rev019.htm#011).md). The prophecy here passes
from the general to the particular, from historic and fulfilled
judgments upon Assyria to the final destruction of all Gentile
world-power at the return of the Lord in glory. (See "Armageddon,";
([Rev 16:14](../../../bib/kjv/rev016.htm#014).md); ([Rev
19:21](../../../bib/kjv/rev019.htm#021).md) "Times of the Gentiles,"; ([Luk
21:24](../../../bib/kjv/luk021.htm#024).md); ([Rev
16:19](../../../bib/kjv/rev016.htm#019).md); "The great tribulation,";
([Psa 2:5](../../../bib/kjv/psa002.htm#005).md); ([Rev
7:14](../../../bib/kjv/rev007.htm#014).md); and

(See Scofield) - ([Isa 13:19](../../../bib/kjv/isa013.htm#019).md).

